# Danh sach Checkbox

> File nay ghi nhan checkbox trong tab Tool va tab Vibe coding.
> Cac tab Subtitle, Partition, Gaming, Driver, Browser, Remote Desktop, Windows va System Information da duoc gom/xoa theo yeu cau.

## Related Files

- @Services/SegmentedDownloadEngine.cs - Download engine: multi-thread segmented (chunk-based)
- @MainWindow.RestoredMethods.cs - Helper methods, shared methods for the entire application

